dimensional.name: Minimum clearance inside covered parking structure

numerical_values.name: Minimum distance for detached covered-parking structure

specs.name: Minimum size for two-car garage or carport

mandatory: Two spaces are required on the lot per dwelling
One of the two spaces must be covered
Clear area for parking space must be free of other uses
conditional_logic: No underground parking garages except by variance
To be considered detached, a covered-parking structure must be a minimum of 3' from the main dwelling
